  <div class="views-field-teaser">
                <div class="field-content"><p>This week China launched its first pilot emission trading program. This development is potentially a major marker in China‚Äôs efforts to reduce greenhouse gas emissions.</p>

<p>The <a href="http://www.sz.gov.cn/cn/xxgk/xwfyr/wqhg/20130521/">Shenzhen Emissions Trading Scheme (ETS)</a> program will cover some 635 industrial companies from 26 industries.  This is the first of seven proposed pilot GHG cap-and-trade schemes in China, which China has been developing since 2011.</p></div>
